title: Boneshaker (1995) Phil Hester Caliber Comics One-Shot
description:
BONESHAKER

By Phillip Hester

Boneshaker- Phil Hester's tale of a wrestler. 

Boneshaker is the story of a suicidal professional wrestler wisked away from earth by a race of aliens who mistakenly believe him to be the most powerful, destructive force in the universe. Both haunting and funny Boneshaker is a story telling experiment that defies classification. Written and drawn by Phillip (Swamp Thing) Hester this one-shot collects the serial from the Harvey Award nominated anthology, Negative Burn.
